OL,3,CCalls for review of 'lenient' sentence
OL,4,Cfor driver who killed two teenagers
OL,6,FAn MP is calling for the Attorney
OL,7,FGeneral to review the sentence of a
OL,8,Fspeeding driver who killed two
OL,9,Fteenagers and seriously injured one
OL,10,Fother when she crashed into their
OL,11,Fstationary car.
OL,13,FNatasha Allarakhia, 34, was travelling
OL,14,Fon the A17 towards Sleaford,
OL,15,FLincolnshire, in June 2024 when she
OL,16,Fploughed into the back of a Ford Festa
OL,17,Fat speed.
