OL,3,CCalls for review of 'lenient' sentence
OL,4,Cfor driver who killed two teenagers
OL,6,FLincoln Crown Court heard she had been
OL,7,Ftaking sips of lager behind the wheel
OL,8,Fand driving at speeds of up to 96
OL,9,Fmiles per hour before the crash.
OL,11,FWilliam Ray, 17, and 18 year-old Eddie
OL,12,FShore, who were in the car Allarakhia
OL,13,Fhit, both died and two other
OL,14,Fpassengers were taken to hospital.
OL,16,FAllarakhia was jailed for 10 years on
OL,17,F18 August after admitting two counts
OL,18,Fof causing death by dangerous driving
OL,19,Fand one of causing serious injury by
OL,20,Fdangerous driving.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
