OL,3,CCalls for review of 'lenient' sentence
OL,4,Cfor driver who killed two teenagers
OL,6,FNow the local MP Caroline Johnson has
OL,7,Fwritten to the Attorney General asking
OL,8,Fhim to review the sentence under the
OL,9,FUnduly Lenient Sentence Scheme.
OL,11,FIn her letter she said: "Allarakhia
OL,12,Freceived a sentence of 10 years, of
OL,13,Fwhich it is possible only two thirds
OL,14,Fwill be served in custody. In my view
OL,15,Fthis sentence does not adequately
OL,16,Freflect the severity of the offences,
OL,17,Fnor the devastating consequences for
OL,18,Fthe victims and their families.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
