OL,3,CCalls for review of 'lenient' sentence
OL,4,Cfor driver who killed two teenagers
OL,6,F"Allarakhia had a high level of
OL,7,Fculpability for this accident, and
OL,8,Fthere are multiple aggravating factors
OL,9,Fwhich significantly outweigh any
OL,10,Fmitigation.
OL,12,F"At the time of the collision,
OL,13,FAllarakhia was driving at 96 mph in a
OL,14,F60pmh zone, and despite multiple
OL,15,Fwarning signs, only initiated braking
OL,16,Fless than two seconds before impact,
OL,17,Fdemonstrating a prolonged lack of
OL,18,Fattention to the road ahead."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/5
