OL,3,CCalls for review of 'lenient' sentence
OL,4,Cfor driver who killed two teenagers
OL,6,FAfter Allarakhia had been jailed,
OL,7,FWilliam Ray's mother Sarah paid
OL,8,Ftribute to him, saying he brought her
OL,9,F"joy, love and hope in everything he
OL,10,Fdid."
OL,12,FA spokesperson for the Attorney
OL,13,FGeneral's Office said: "We have
OL,14,Freceived a request for this sentence
OL,15,Fto be considered under the Unduly
OL,16,FLenient Sentence (ULS) scheme. The Law
OL,17,FOfficers have 28 days from sentencing
OL,18,Fto consider the case and make a
OL,19,Fdecision."
